metadata.dc:author: Jacques Grimonster, L
Enrique Fernández, M
metadata.dc:description: The authors analyse the biomechanical bases of the Kratochvil "retentive complex" and show how they have induced the nowadays north-american propositions (RPI & RPA). They compare them to the european ones (Nally-Martinet).
metadata.dc:title: Retención y biomecánica de los "complejos retentivos". III Parte: La escuela de Kratochvil y complejos retentivos "actuales".
[Retention and biomechanics of retentive complexes. 3. The Kratochvil school and current retentive complexes].
